.TP
\f[B]-l\f[R], \f[B]\[en]list\f[R]
List conversation files in \[ti]/.dejavu.
.TP
\f[B]-c\f[R], \f[B]\[en]cmd `cmd'\f[R]
Execute `cmd' on entry to D\['e]j\[`a]Vu.
